00:25:37.741 --> 00:25:39.340
LEE DANIEL KRAVETZ:
Yeah, it was fun.

00:25:39.340 --> 00:25:44.270
DAN ARIELY: And so if you
think about supersurvivors,

00:25:44.270 --> 00:25:47.240
how much of it is
